OL,3,CHolidaymakers hit by above-inflation
OL,4,Crises in cost of summer trips `
OL,5,Canalysis
OL,7,FEuropean package holidays are up to
OL,8,F11.5% more expensive this year
OL,9,Fcompared with 2024, according to new
OL,10,Fanalysis.
OL,12,FConsumer group Which? said this is
OL,13,Fbecause of a range of factors,
OL,14,Fincluding high demand, rising energy
OL,15,Fcosts for hotels, and capacity
OL,16,Fconstraints for airlines.
