OL,3,CHolidaymakers hit by above-inflation
OL,4,Crises in cost of summer trips `
OL,5,Canalysis
OL,7,FThe analysis took into account prices
OL,8,Ffor more than 8,000 European package
OL,9,Fholidays, comparing bookings made this
OL,10,Fmonth for an August departure with
OL,11,Fbookings made in January 2024 for an
OL,12,FAugust 2024 departure.
OL,14,FIt found trips to the Black Sea coast
OL,15,Fof Bulgaria have seen the most
OL,16,Fsignificant increase.
OL,18,FThe average per person price for a
OL,19,Fseven-day break in that location has
OL,20,Frisen by 11.5% from #1,038 to #1,157.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
