OL,5,Canalysis
OL,7,FThat means a couple will have to find
OL,8,Fan extra #238 on average to make a
OL,9,Fbooking.
OL,11,FOther destinations with high average
OL,12,Fprice rises were found to be Italy (up
OL,13,F7.4%), Portugal (up 6.8%) and Cyprus
OL,14,F(up 6.4%).
OL,16,FAcross all locations, the average
OL,17,Fincrease was 4.2%.
