OL,4,Crises in cost of summer trips `
OL,5,Canalysis
OL,7,FWhich? said this is compared with the
OL,8,FUK's Consumer Prices Index measure of
OL,9,Finflation of 2.5% in the year to
OL,10,FDecember 2024, whereas the rate of
OL,11,Finflation in the euro area was 2.4%.
OL,13,FPackage holiday prices have fallen in
OL,14,Fjust a handful of hotspots, such as
OL,15,FIbiza (down 6.4%) and Tenerife (down
OL,16,F2.0%).
